<li class='cover' id='bookCover_19400580'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/19400580-sycamore-row"><img alt="Sycamore Row: by John Grisham -- Analysis" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1386881200l/19400580._SX98_.jpg" />
